    <h1>Lasagna</h1>

    <img src="https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/lasagna-image-tomato.jpg" alt="Delicious Lasagna" width="400">

    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>This lasagna is a cheesy, meaty, and flavorful dish that is perfect for dinner.</p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Lasagna noodles</li>
        <li>Ground beef</li>
        <li>Tomato sauce</li>
        <li>Mozzarella cheese</li>
        <li>Parmesan cheese</li>
        <li>Italian seasoning</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Cook lasagna noodles according to package instructions.</li>
        <li>Brown ground beef and mix with tomato sauce and seasoning.</li>
        <li>Layer noodles, meat sauce, ricotta, and mozzarella in a baking dish.</li>
        <li>Bake at 375°F (190°C) for 45 minutes.</li>
        <li>Let rest for 15 minutes before serving.</li>
    </ol>
